Paper: hep-th/9611015

Date: 1996-11-04

Title: Non Local Observables and Confinement in BF Formulation of Yang-Mills

TheoryAuthors: Francesco Fucito, Maurizio Martellini and Mauro Zeni

Comments: 11pages, latex, contribution to Cargese Summer School 96

The vev's of the magnetic order-disorder operators in QCD are found in anexplicit calculation using the first order formulation of Yang-Mills theory.